---
title: Roasted Salmon and Veggie Salad with Bulgar and Feta
description: We love good Salmon with Veggies, Bulgar & Feta and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roasted-salmon-and-veggie-salad-6d1be643-1d9487d8.jpg
